%F A349221 T(n, k) = [k|binomial(n-1, k-1)] = Sum_{j>=1} [k|binomial(n-1, k-1) AND gcd(n, k) = j], n >= 1, 1 <= k <= n, where [] is the Iverson bracket. (The j = 1 case is A054521.)
%F A349221 T(n, k) = T(n, n-k), n > 1, 1 <= k < n.
